<li class="py-1.5 border-b border-slate-100 last:border-0 flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500 mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span><span>7 月计划环比 +0.1%（较 6 月实际 +1.4%），供给收缩信号初现。</span></li>
