<li class="py-1.5 border-b border-slate-100 last:border-0 flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500 mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span><span>环保政策放松（落后产能复产）</span></li>
