<li class="py-1.5 border-b border-slate-100 last:border-0 flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500 mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span><span><strong class="font-bold text-slate-900">锑</strong>：华锡有色、湖南黄金（资源紧缺+海外大矿减产）</span></li>
